        - Report Info: Chuẩn Bị (Part IV) -> Goal: Instruct -> Presentation: Step-by-step text sections in 'Chuẩn Bị' (Assessment, Color Choice, Patch Test, Tools) -> Interaction: Read, follow steps -> Justification: Practical guidance.
